{"tid":1080543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔工業邨情困女車內燒炭亡","createTime":"2019-03-27T16:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T17:22:20.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"967ad198714657d7ae8da4f515ce29e440ae12ad","tid":1080543,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"大埔工業邨大盛街，晚上7時許，有途人發現一部停泊於咪錶位的客貨車內有人昏迷，於是報警求助。消防接報到場，擊破車窗打開車門，發現一名女子昏迷倒卧車內，經救護員檢驗證實她已氣絕身亡。警方封鎖現場調查，在車內發現一盆燒過的炭，並有一封遺書，正調查原因。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，死者姓林（39歲），昨日因感情問題與男友爭執，其後她揚言去自殺，並駕駛客貨車離去。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=acfc8d0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190327/59419790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190327%2F59419790&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=7c1cdcc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190327%2F59419790&h=1ca9e221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190327/59419790</a>"},{"pid":"d1fc9e0a24bf475cef5c87867a1f11a380455f2e","tid":1080543,"uid":130695,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"講得出做得到，好過成班豬閪日日叫春"},{"pid":"9dfff49161af281c79e573fc5946d9a3620292ec","tid":1080543,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:25:35.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係死係屋入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br